n "description" fields they might encounter during the GitHub Pages setup process.</div><div class="paragraph">I should cover:</div><ul start="1"><li><div class="paragraph">Repo description</div></li><li><div class="paragraph">Commit message</div></li><li><div class="paragraph">README content (brief)</div></li><li><div class="paragraph">Page description/meta</div></li></ul><div class="paragraph">I'll answer in French since the user asked in French.</div></div></div></div></div> </div></div></div></div> <!----><!----> <div data-v-b3358103="" data-v-5f641036="" class="markdown-container"><div data-v-b3358103="" class="markdown"><div class="paragraph">Voici ce que vous pouvez écrire dans les différents champs <strong>Description</strong> lors du setup :</div><hr><h2 class="">1️⃣ Description du repo (sur GitHub)</h2><div class="paragraph">Dans le champ <em>"Description"</em> lors de la création du repo, écrivez :</div><blockquote><div class="paragraph"><strong>Portfolio Data Analyst — Mamadou Kamara</strong></div><div class="paragraph">Portfolio interactif présentant mes projets en data analytics, business intelligence et healthcare analytics. Construit avec HTML/CSS/JS vanilla et hébergé sur GitHub Pages.</div></blockquote><hr><h2 class="">2️⃣ Message de commit (quand vous uploadez <code data-v-782faaad="" data-v-b3358103="" class="segment-code-inline">index.html</code>)</h2><div class="paragraph">Dans le champ <em>"Commit changes"</em>, écrivez :</div><blockquote><div class="paragraph"><code data-v-782faaad="" data-v-b3358103="" class="segment-code-inline">feat: ajout du portfolio v1.0</code></div></blockquote><div class="paragraph">Ou simplement :</div><blockquote><div class="paragraph"><code data-v-782faaad="" data-v-b3358103="" class="segment-code-inline">Ajout du portfolio HTML</code></div></blockquote><hr><h2 class="">3️⃣ README.md (si vous en avez créé un)</h2><div class="paragraph">Voici un template minimal à copier-coller :</div><div data-v-4ebffd48="" data-v-